<p><a href="http://www.woshipm.com/ucd/3732496.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">信息输入框的交互思考</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.woshipm.com/pd/878454.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">小小输入框背后隐藏的潜规则</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/aba4bf4de862" target="_blank" rel="noopener">优化输入框，让填写如丝般顺滑</a></p>
<p><a href="https://uxmovement.com/forms/why-you-shouldnt-use-solid-or-underlined-text-fields/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">为什么不应该使用实线或带下划线的文本字段</a></p>
